Package: Eliat
Title: Tools for Retrieving, Processing, and Exporting GenBank Sequence Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Fernando Joel",
      family = "Castro",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "fernandocastro203@yahoo.com"
    )
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for downloading GenBank nucleotide sequences,
    extracting rich metadata (taxonomy, geography, specimen details, etc.),
    and exporting results in multiple formats (CSV, GenBank flatfile, Shapefile,
    GeoTIFF). Includes utilities for spatial rasterization and biodiversity
    richness modeling.
